            <h4 class="h4 text-dark" style="font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">What amount can I expect?</h4>
            <p style="margin:0 0 14px; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6; color:#334155;">PLEASE NOTE that our offer is not a vehicle valuation. Estimates from online car marketplaces may not accurately reflect your car's value within the dealership network. Even though we strive to offer as much as possible, as a dealership, the prices we offer are similar to wholesale or trade-in prices.</p>
            <h4 class="h4 text-dark" style="font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">My offer is too low?</h4>
            <p style="margin:0 0 14px; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6; color:#334155;">If our offer doesn’t meet your expectations, there’s no obligation to accept. However, please keep us in mind for any future opportunities, as car values often fluctuate over time. We may be able to better align with your expectations on your next vehicle. Remember that our offers are valid for 7 days from the date they are made, giving you ample time to consider your options.</p>
          </td>
          <td class="stack col" width="50%" style="padding:0 0 0 10px;">
            <h4 class="h4 text-dark" style="font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">How is the offer calculated?</h4>
            <p style="margin:0 0 14px; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6; color:#334155;">Our experienced buying team determines your offer by assessing current market conditions, including factors like supply and demand. We rely on up-to-date, reliable national resources for this assessment, and because market conditions can change, our offers are valid for 7 days.</p>
            <h4 class="h4 text-dark" style="font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Can my offer change?</h4>
            <p style="margin:0; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6; color:#334155;">Your offer may change based on our inspection of your vehicle. If any mechanical or cosmetic repairs and/or maintenance are required, it may be accounted for in our final offer. If no additional work is needed, you'll receive the full offer. Any damages or work you've already disclosed will be factored into the maximum offer you'll receive via email.</p>
